review: Hello ....wanna share my experience with mk dental ...mainly with doctors over there r completely well experienced the way they explain the treatment z outstanding even a common man can understand what procedure they r performing ,mostly cost is very reasonable n my special thanks to Dr.sravani n Dr.mohan krishna...for taking treatment very responsible...n followups n very good  tq.......

I highly recommend my friends n family to visit MK Dental n consult Dr Mohan Krishna.

I have wisdom tooth pain,went for MK Dental. Underwent treatment with Dr. Mohan Krishna and Dr. Sravani. They handled the treatment in a easy manner without any pain I strongly recommend mk dental for the best treatment .....
